ython","CNN-LSTM","MediaPipe","Computer Vision"],"github":"","external":"","video":"/isl_demo.mp4","cover":null},"html":"<p>Converts live hand-sign video into text using MediaPipe key-point extraction feeding a CNN-LSTM model achieving greater than 94% accuracy. Designed and trained the end-to-end pipeline for real-time inference on streaming video input.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Canadian Rental Price Predictor","tech":["Python","Flask","scikit-learn","XGBoost","Pandas"],"github":"https://github.com/omair2200/portfolio/tree/main/content/projects/housing-price-predictor","external":"/housing-predictor","video":null,"cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/portfolio/static/c7fc9842077e89925f226157a87a0d7e/eadd3/house-price-banner.png","srcSet":"/portfolio/static/c7fc9842077e89925f226157a87a0d7e/e9a79/house-price-banner.png 160w,\n/portfolio/static/c7fc9842077e89925f226157a87a0d7e/5f035/house-price-banner.png 320w,\n/portfolio/static/c7fc9842077e89925f226157a87a0d7e/eadd3/house-price-banner.png 640w","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/portfolio/static/c7fc9842077e89925f226157a87a0d7e/6de5b/house-price-banner.avif 160w,\n/portfolio/static/c7fc9842077e89925f226157a87a0d7e/20389/house-price-banner.avif 320w,\n/portfolio/static/c7fc9842077e89925f226157a87a0d7e/8c32c/house-price-banner.avif 640w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/portfolio/static/c7fc9842077e89925f226157a87a0d7e/60b4d/house-price-banner.webp 160w,\n/portfolio/static/c7fc9842077e89925f226157a87a0d7e/5e011/house-price-banner.webp 320w,\n/portfolio/static/c7fc9842077e89925f226157a87a0d7e/90d07/house-price-banner.webp 640w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":700}}}},"html":"<p>ML-powered rental price estimator for the Canadian real estate market. Users input province